raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: You there babe?
Player: I'm here
Player: Thank god it's Friday
Mabel: Yeah haha, you must be exhausted 😅
Mabel: So uhm...
Mabel: About the party
Mabel: img: mabel/142
Player: Cute!
Player: Something on your mind?
Mabel: I'm just wondering that everyone seemed cool about... uhm...
Mabel: That kissing game Naomi talked about
Mabel: But eh, we haven't even.. y'know...
Mabel: Kissed 👉👈
Mabel: And that maybe we're both gonna end up kissing other people??
Mabel: So I'm a little confused by this whole thing 😅
Mabel: Aren't you? 😶
- What if I was okay with it? 😗
	set Story.flag = \"NTSNoKiss\"
	Player: What if I was okay with it?
	Mabel: Okay with what exactly?? 😳
	Player: With you kissing someone else at the party
	Mabel: ...
	Mabel: Excuse me?? 😀
	do heart(1)
	Mabel: Is the babe I know still there?
	Player: I'm here, think about it 😆 Might be fun
	Mabel: But... we haven't even had ours yet 🥺
	Player: I know
	Player: That kinda makes it more exciting honestly
	Mabel: WHAT 😳
	Mabel: Thought: Is he serious right now??
	Mabel: Thought: My boyfriend wants me to kiss someone else before him??
	Mabel: Babe that's...
	Mabel: You're messing with me right
	Player: I'm totally not
	do heart(2)
	Player: A mystery kiss with someone you don't know 
	Player: That sounds thrilling to you?
	do echo_set([\"143\"])
	Mabel: I mean...
	Mabel: Thought: Why is my heart racing
	Mabel: It does sound kind of intense, like in my movies 🙈
	- That's the spirit 😏
		Player: That's the spirit 😏
		Mabel: I didn't say yes!! 😤
		Mabel: But...
		Mabel: Thought: But I didn't say no either
		Mabel: If it's just a game then... I guess it's fine? 🙈
		Mabel: You really won't be jealous?
		Player: Not even a little
		Mabel: Thought: Something about that is weirdly exciting
		Mabel: Okay...
		Mabel: I'll try to keep an open mind about it 😶
		Mabel: But if it's weird I'm blaming you!!
		Player: Deal 😄
	- You might even like it more than kissing me
		Player: You might even like it more than kissing me 😆
		Mabel: No way!! 😤
		Mabel: That's impossible
		Mabel: Thought: ...right?
		Mabel: I'm sure yours will be way better
		Player: Guess we'll find out after then 😉
		Mabel: Thought: After?? Not before??
		Mabel: Wait you don't wanna kiss before the party?
		Player: Where's the fun in that?
		Mabel: 😶
		Mabel: Thought: So my first kiss is really going to be with...
		Mabel: Thought: This is crazy.. my head is rushing...
		Mabel: You're unbelievable 🫠
		Mabel: But fine!! 😤
		Mabel: Don't come crying to me after 🙈
	do echo_clear()
	do heart(1)
	Mabel: Anyway it's getting late
	Mabel: I should probably sleep
	Mabel: Or not sleep after what I have to think about today 🫠
	Player: 😂
	Mabel: Goodnight babe 😘
	Player: Night 😊
	do heart(0)
- Maybe we should have ours first? 😌
	set Story.flag = \"NTSKiss\"
	Player: Maybe we should have ours first? 😌
	Mabel: Really?? 😳
	Mabel: I mean.. sure 😎
	Player: Are you okay? 😀
	Mabel: Totally fine!
	Mabel: Thought: AHHHHH
	Mabel: So uhm... when? 👉👈
	Player: Weekend seems busy so.. maybe tonight?
	Player: I could come over
	Mabel: Wait.. tonight?
	Mabel: To my dorm?? 😳
	do heart(1)
	do echo_set([\"144\"])
	Mabel: Thought: Oh god that's.. not a bad idea
	- If that's okay with you
		Player: If that's okay with you
		Mabel: Thought: Yessss!!
		Mabel: Yeah that's fine with me
		Player: 😘
		Mabel: Shut up 😭
	- Unless you wanna come to me? 😁
		Player: Unless you wanna come to me? 😁
		Mabel: Whaaat?
		Mabel: Your place is so far though 😗
		Mabel: Mine is okay 👀
		Player: But we're the same distance from each other 😂
		Mabel: But you know.. it'll be dark and stuff
		Mabel: img: mabel/142
		Player: Fine haha
		Player: Works for me
	Mabel: Thought: Our first kiss before the party
	Mabel: Thought: This is so crazy but
	Mabel: Thought: At least I won't be going in completely clueless
	do echo_clear()
	do heart(2)
	Mabel: WAIT so you're coming now??
	Mabel: Now now?
	Mabel: Like right now??
	Player: Yuh
	Mabel: I need to clean my room omg
	Player: Haha don't worry about it
	Mabel: I totally will 🥺
	do heart(1)
	Player: I'll be on my way soon
	Mabel: 😱
	Mabel: I have an hour to prepare.. I don't have anything omg!
	Player: See you soon 😉😂
	Mabel: Jeeeeeeeeez 😩
	do heart(0)
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
